{"tid":21862,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我地整咗個免費學習平台","createTime":"2016-12-04T06:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T20:55:03.000Z","uid":52832,"like":122,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a519d66503a9a5b6f995c1a0a43a0083cea712c4","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://project-identity.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproject-identity.hk&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9fa4cace\" target=\"_blank\">http://project-identity.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n我地最近整咗個叫 IDENTITY 嘅免費學習平台，以教學影片為主，目前涵蓋咗初中至高中必修數學嘅大小課題。我地嘅理念好簡單，就係想整一個屬於香港學生嘅免費學習平台，而數學科就係試探方向嘅第一步。<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個都冇 programming 背景，個網站只係用 WordPress 砌積木砌出嚟，而且暫時都係搵平平地嘅 shared hosting 裝住個網，所以速度上效能上有咩不足請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我地網站嘅簡介短片，有興趣就望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAbISOUJJRoQ&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1144d966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ</a>"},{"pid":"ab2a58a0ce1913ee147a8b18915884130feaae8e","tid":21862,"uid":53269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"正呀， 多謝brother,  我有煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，想拎4可以點操？"},{"pid":"ed1416dca987450043bea86d509191e0e278388c","tid":21862,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:03:38.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffdd1c7858ac7cf115edc9c019eb5420c46cc8d","tid":21862,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquo