gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，想拎4可以點操？</blockquote><br />\n睇佢個網主要集中係教concept 好有心 但係你要有心讀或者係中4中5比較好<br />\n考skill補底方法就少左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講得冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地嘅方向唔係諗住教 skills，因為 skills 嘅話有好多有心人喺 YouTube 都有分享到，而且我地始終好天真咁覺得，明白概念嘅話，其餘嘅你會自己搞得掂</blockquote><br />\n好多人都未必真係想讀數 只求一個好d既grade 真係想讀個d 都會靠自己識哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢條路難行"},{"pid":"ec8ee6c157131b7a6794aa6e2adc3048a766018f","tid":21862,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1b5ed0a0d2b54f10c298c7a9855e014350cbe7","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正呀， 多謝brother,  我有煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，想拎4可以點操？</blockquote><br />\n睇佢個網主要集中係教concept 好有心 但係你要有心讀或者係中4中5比較好<br />\n考skill補底方法就少左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講得冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地嘅方向唔係諗住教 skills，因為 skills 嘅話有好多有心人喺 YouTube 都有分享到，而且我地始終好天真咁覺得，明白概念嘅話，其餘嘅你會自己搞得掂</blockquote><br />\n好多人都未必真係想讀數 只求一個好d既grade 真係想讀個d 都會靠自己識哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢條路難行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有心理準備唔係個個受落㗎喇，但我地唔係諗住賺錢，冇所謂啦。同埋我地喺 IDENTITY 個「關於我們」度都提到，我地想做老師嘅 flipped classroom 資源庫，所以我地一定係行 concept 路線。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔知咩係 flipped classroom 嘅話，去 wikipedia 望下：<br />\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flipped_classroom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFlipped_classroom&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=585a9ecd\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flipped_classroom</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%BF%BB%E8%BD%AC%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%25BD%25AC%25E8%25AF%25BE%25E5%25A0%2582&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b0588342\" target=\"_blank\">http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%BF%BB%E8%BD%AC%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82</a>"},{"pid":"4c5d4acdf6cce1679b2e9b879ae399a4d6b13cc0","tid":21862,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正呀， 多謝brother,  我有煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，想拎4可以點操？</blockquote><br />\n睇佢個網主要集中係教concept 好有心 但係你要有心讀或者係中4中5比較好<br />\n考skill補底方法就少左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講得冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地嘅方向唔係諗住教 skills，因為 skills 嘅話有好多有心人喺 YouTube 都有分享到，而且我地始終好天真咁覺得，明白概念嘅話，其餘嘅你會自己搞得掂</blockquote><br />\n好多人都未必真係想讀數 只求一個好d既grade 真係想讀個d 都會靠自己識哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢條路難行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都有心理準備唔係個個受落㗎喇，但我地唔係諗住賺錢，冇所謂啦。同埋我地喺 IDENTITY 個「關於我們」度都提到，我地想做老師嘅 flipped classroom 資源庫，所以我地一定係行 concept 路線。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔知咩係 flipped classroom 嘅話，去 wikipedia 望下：<br />\n<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flipped_classroom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFlipped_classroom&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=585a9ecd\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flipped_classroom</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%BF%BB%E8%BD%AC%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E8%25BD%25AC%25E8%25AF%25BE%25E5%25A0%2582&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b0588342\" target=\"_blank\">http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%BF%BB%E8%BD%AC%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好有心 支持你地 呢種方式幾理想"},{"pid":"e7268a38b2d587b497f782ea2ddd687debcf1e2e","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880c5520e7ec971433b23c2e528e854f8ad74d96","tid":21862,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:23:35.000Z","msg":"會唔會教埋m2?"},{"pid":"05d0302bca8c062c58f1c3d14e953dde4254da18","tid":21862,"uid":36107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b73f3192febde663a166598a7721662b6879fd52","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會教埋m2?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地想呀，但要睇下大家對 IDENTITY 反應如何，再睇下而家個方向有冇行錯先。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我地淨係整中一至中六 complusory math 都用咗一年半時間，就算而家即刻開始整 M1 M2，相信都要等多一年，所以對唔住喇，短期內真係做唔到住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e198dcdfa9fd44ddffffee286f16314f8ca7091e","tid":21862,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"支持巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a201f02a0acf3826219c58125634ab509ef54532","tid":21862,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會教埋m2?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地想呀，但要睇下大家對 IDENTITY 反應如何，再睇下而家個方向有冇行錯先。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我地淨係整中一至中六 complusory math 都用咗一年半時間，就算而家即刻開始整 M1 M2，相信都要等多一年，所以對唔住喇，短期內真係做唔到住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328981306cdb102b04dc8462347f911326274dec","tid":21862,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:20:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"964139b2847bc7619cfc85ec3d8b64d93a8dee88","tid":21862,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://project-identity.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproject-identity.hk&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9fa4cace\" target=\"_blank\">http://project-identity.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n我地最近整咗個叫 IDENTITY 嘅免費學習平台，以教學影片為主，目前涵蓋咗初中至高中必修數學嘅大小課題。我地嘅理念好簡單，就係想整一個屬於香港學生嘅免費學習平台，而數學科就係試探方向嘅第一步。<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個都冇 programming 背景，個網站只係用 WordPress 砌積木砌出嚟，而且暫時都係搵平平地嘅 shared hosting 裝住個網，所以速度上效能上有咩不足請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我地網站嘅簡介短片，有興趣就望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAbISOUJJRoQ&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1144d966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT 巴打我有冇野可以幫手？"},{"pid":"3d59fbdb45799aa3f151bce42a3e1dbc629b1ac9","tid":21862,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"有冇得教埋大學數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af009b1da4814ae9ab084de43faf5e7367899fa","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://project-identity.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproject-identity.hk&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9fa4cace\" target=\"_blank\">http://project-identity.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n我地最近整咗個叫 IDENTITY 嘅免費學習平台，以教學影片為主，目前涵蓋咗初中至高中必修數學嘅大小課題。我地嘅理念好簡單，就係想整一個屬於香港學生嘅免費學習平台，而數學科就係試探方向嘅第一步。<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個都冇 programming 背景，個網站只係用 WordPress 砌積木砌出嚟，而且暫時都係搵平平地嘅 shared hosting 裝住個網，所以速度上效能上有咩不足請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我地網站嘅簡介短片，有興趣就望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAbISOUJJRoQ&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1144d966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT 巴打我有冇野可以幫手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打多謝你份心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時就冇乜大問題（或者只係我地察覺唔到），係有啲功能想加落去但唔識整。不過我地唔想貿貿然搵巴打你做義工，我地都過意唔去。<br />\n<br />\n反正而家都係 launch 咗冇耐，就比個平台運作一輪再作打算啦。話說有另一位巴打都專登 send email 過嚟話想幫手，好多謝你地咁有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ccd2035876e89ccc54e565adfc9f95073567de","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇得教埋大學數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n太睇得起我地幾個喇，我地唔係 major 數學，只係同數學都叫做有些少關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72ee8fafd814bcaa76a06b5ae0aef76174360e6","tid":21862,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"l m"},{"pid":"f5e7796e20d300ed1a3dbe7b68e779f7c8926c8d","tid":21862,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:02:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"dbe27391d3a053d5a49e56316b2afa341fcf7090","tid":21862,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"巴打你好<br />\n我都搞緊相同既野<br />\n有興趣可以交流下"},{"pid":"23645b726f7090f05afeff1a65621f68342425db","tid":21862,"uid":37447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"幫pish"},{"pid":"6e2e4adbc72ea2b88fb181bf7368296d74ddb2fd","tid":21862,"uid":36952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT 巴打我有冇野可以幫手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇方法聯絡到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d523f40844732947ba077315fcf4a95395b10a5","tid":21862,"uid":11677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7fd470e9c8b60dc843f48a65a621185f97e8b96e","tid":21862,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"不如寫個粵文嘅關於我們..."},{"pid":"6e04abe752f968a563ef6daff000539c285fed0c","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你好<br />\n我都搞緊相同既野<br />\n有興趣可以交流下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有興趣傾嘅話 email 我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncontact@project-identity.hk"},{"pid":"a46fa5aa5cee2fd248da7f98c8d8e13d07bf46aa","tid":21862,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"u sci 留名<br />\n睇下其他科幫唔幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d58688e9806d0cf26dffcc45c10f6cd18280f7","tid":21862,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:39:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aad2bcba831787456489799e4a121ac6c52f6fbd","tid":21862,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"正到暈。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c296dba422015a50d762fbc99388ba5be1bd0d8","tid":21862,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇得教埋大學數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係就最好，我會好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eff6f9a71fadd48e3048898122bb6a05443458b","tid":21862,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"bc1e4c13f69d51ce1453445074fc089cf0165f31","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇得教埋大學數<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係就最好，我會好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就等更加有能力嘅人去做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34796a44dd5783199d5ed771b17968d52a59c286","tid":21862,"uid":12137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:27:06.000Z","msg":"留名幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc834e4a973982ec0ea717b27b603bcc972ba85","tid":21862,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5668fb225b46ea28a527d3a27b8f274c3c3b6f29","tid":21862,"uid":2285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6e593a74e054e43df25191b596ac41ce68b93fd4","tid":21862,"uid":47926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"醫療科留名 有野可以幫巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f635a317f5b22007234d78d5486690cacbcb8f7c","tid":21862,"uid":38831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"好欣賞巴打你哋咁有心"},{"pid":"c99d2bb9c4d3ed00c62a57e096582cb0c531395e","tid":21862,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6031e59c1ee7f1f9e1f38a77b5c0d66169ed1983","tid":21862,"uid":49041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"afab72dea7a0c142f0ed3a4a0998b9cc1bb7f6b5","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d4b5248c4882a858cc85ee204ab11ce7af0d1e","tid":21862,"uid":7656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://project-identity.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproject-identity.hk&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9fa4cace\" target=\"_blank\">http://project-identity.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n我地最近整咗個叫 IDENTITY 嘅免費學習平台，以教學影片為主，目前涵蓋咗初中至高中必修數學嘅大小課題。我地嘅理念好簡單，就係想整一個屬於香港學生嘅免費學習平台，而數學科就係試探方向嘅第一步。<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個都冇 programming 背景，個網站只係用 WordPress 砌積木砌出嚟，而且暫時都係搵平平地嘅 shared hosting 裝住個網，所以速度上效能上有咩不足請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我地網站嘅簡介短片，有興趣就望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAbISOUJJRoQ&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1144d966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT 巴打我有冇野可以幫手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打多謝你份心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時就冇乜大問題（或者只係我地察覺唔到），係有啲功能想加落去但唔識整。不過我地唔想貿貿然搵巴打你做義工，我地都過意唔去。<br />\n<br />\n反正而家都係 launch 咗冇耐，就比個平台運作一輪再作打算啦。話說有另一位巴打都專登 send email 過嚟話想幫手，好多謝你地咁有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我上年先至啱啱大學畢業，而家讀緊Master，咁既然你地都係免費教人，我都好樂意去同你地一齊搞搞個website，其實我而家係澳洲讀緊，依家去到二月中都係放緊summer break。所以呢段時間都好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87294cae9edf82e602e5d81237fdbccb196c519c","tid":21862,"uid":8942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"12726b2a5ed96203b34abd8601a30270d5056cbf","tid":21862,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc09904cbd9a04786589a24f251ca9e9f3a194f7","tid":21862,"uid":25885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:37:44.000Z","msg":"三大數學系留名<br />\n<br />\n可以幫手出片教高中Chem, 如果有野幫到手記得出聲!"},{"pid":"a0ca727af807f514c060c45087b7f44c232255d0","tid":21862,"uid":49183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"084026abb8aa2af665c38e3feee8bd386132ae10","tid":21862,"uid":7889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打好有心，支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a85e77927791f2ff6dcf377cd092a6774266643","tid":21862,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"570af5de510d1b71ed211c0342b7ade4eebdf0d2","tid":21862,"uid":53499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2ccdf6d8f3811c3e7ab32340503e9bc6dc85a09d","tid":21862,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35a253ff4abbd20c7b6f7456d5902803d78b9b4","tid":21862,"uid":36750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"唔駛想潑冷水，不過覺得herman yeung同你地做既野好似差唔多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659d3c2b711b17f0d44469dd11c22801dbbf7974","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三大數學系留名<br />\n<br />\n可以幫手出片教高中Chem, 如果有野幫到手記得出聲!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多謝你同其他巴打咁有心，但我地都唔想無緣無故要你地做義工，始終工作量真係好大，唔係幾個月就完成得到嘅事嚟，所以其他科目嘅片仍然有待計劃。"},{"pid":"08af9d13635fdcc30ff686af68c63b0f9780fec1","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔駛想潑冷水，不過覺得herman yeung同你地做既野好似差唔多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會係冷水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我地一直都有留意香港有冇類似嘅平台，所以當然有留意開 Herman Yeung。佢真係非常之有心，我地付出嘅極其量都係時間，佢就直頭放棄埋原本份人工。<br />\n<br />\nHerman Yeung 嘅片好多都好有質素，但我地喺影片設計、課題結構等好多細節都有自己諗法。數學科就係幫其他科試探呢啲諗法嘅先頭卒。<br />\n<br />\n另外我想讚多 Herman Yeung 一樣嘢，佢口齒真係好伶俐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地啲片係靠大量剪接先做到咁流暢，我本身講嘢係 1999。佢喺冇剪接嘅情況底下都可以講得咁順，呢樣我點學都學唔識。"},{"pid":"c0be19e8980e0724323ec8eb783d0fda575289b5","tid":21862,"uid":54875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"路過都要支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26330ad8ecf9cb9b964ff3c078a8dc5f3b1d76a","tid":21862,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:59:16.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d8949081819522d4478af5e7c8e07655a6f9a324","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://project-identity.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproject-identity.hk&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9fa4cace\" target=\"_blank\">http://project-identity.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n我地最近整咗個叫 IDENTITY 嘅免費學習平台，以教學影片為主，目前涵蓋咗初中至高中必修數學嘅大小課題。我地嘅理念好簡單，就係想整一個屬於香港學生嘅免費學習平台，而數學科就係試探方向嘅第一步。<br />\n<br />\n我地幾個都冇 programming 背景，個網站只係用 WordPress 砌積木砌出嚟，而且暫時都係搵平平地嘅 shared hosting 裝住個網，所以速度上效能上有咩不足請見諒。<br />\n<br />\n下面係我地網站嘅簡介短片，有興趣就望下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAbISOUJJRoQ&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1144d966\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AbISOUJJRoQ</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT 巴打我有冇野可以幫手？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打多謝你份心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時就冇乜大問題（或者只係我地察覺唔到），係有啲功能想加落去但唔識整。不過我地唔想貿貿然搵巴打你做義工，我地都過意唔去。<br />\n<br />\n反正而家都係 launch 咗冇耐，就比個平台運作一輪再作打算啦。話說有另一位巴打都專登 send email 過嚟話想幫手，好多謝你地咁有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我上年先至啱啱大學畢業，而家讀緊Master，咁既然你地都係免費教人，我都好樂意去同你地一齊搞搞個website，其實我而家係澳洲讀緊，依家去到二月中都係放緊summer break。所以呢段時間都好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遺憾巴打多謝你。你介唔介意 email 我地，或者我地喺 email 度傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncontact@project-identity.hk"},{"pid":"c76f94e9e91b3f88b6396f14ae86ac10cc4d78eb","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968a4d37e0f6ff7d480454acc95aa4dc86caabe2","tid":21862,"uid":35572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"一鍵留名"},{"pid":"af9e5afac3cae19732815a6779bfb42b611025c9","tid":21862,"uid":50193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港正正需要D咁既嘢"},{"pid":"0fefe6d2c06c5d5e4254c1ff9f1627c4007e7354","tid":21862,"uid":9749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1971bee116e3de8ffc72a52dc23876d2308e5c36","tid":21862,"uid":36895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"支持Bro<br />\n<br />\n你地有無IT Support，我可以幫手<br />\n個網站都幾多Vulnerability<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18445cb4ccc9bf52eb80ba8025b204cf553447ff","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持Bro<br />\n<br />\n你地有無IT Support，我可以幫手<br />\n個網站都幾多Vulnerability<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀，所以完全唔識搞 security <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係可以一次搞掂定係定期維護嘅問題？"},{"pid":"d006758b19647e6b53b5996c4fc1691cad000bc2","tid":21862,"uid":53674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔駛想潑冷水，不過覺得herman yeung同你地做既野好似差唔多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會係冷水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我地一直都有留意香港有冇類似嘅平台，所以當然有留意開 Herman Yeung。佢真係非常之有心，我地付出嘅極其量都係時間，佢就直頭放棄埋原本份人工。<br />\n<br />\nHerman Yeung 嘅片好多都好有質素，但我地喺影片設計、課題結構等好多細節都有自己諗法。數學科就係幫其他科試探呢啲諗法嘅先頭卒。<br />\n<br />\n另外我想讚多 Herman Yeung 一樣嘢，佢口齒真係好伶俐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地啲片係靠大量剪接先做到咁流暢，我本身講嘢係 1999。佢喺冇剪接嘅情況底下都可以講得咁順，呢樣我點學都學唔識。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n偶像herman yeung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e6b64670282187f8863582060d7c4df1c3a58c","tid":21862,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:38:20.000Z","msg":"推一推先"},{"pid":"0ceaed8740cf53d7692ee06ad6070953a7be00d3","tid":21862,"uid":18877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T19:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d510a573160da8ff6ea300d47fa9fd4eca2a1ddc","tid":21862,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbe00e9733f72b6cd843d609e77c8ca2097460c","tid":21862,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7f68d78a0cc94021acdb07abdc1117deede440","tid":21862,"uid":328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一定要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c45561401646c8e681733787065aadab98f733","tid":21862,"uid":59861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"如果有大學數就好"},{"pid":"90451566c143489c514f34c1e536bc3398a57243","tid":21862,"uid":11571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:20:32.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"28518244f090e33f679b4d4a63b392309cfbdd4a","tid":21862,"uid":11571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"最鍾意免費野"},{"pid":"f531bb4a83207673f2901e81313fb0989aa0fe1c","tid":21862,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10a98348d