","tid":21862,"uid":27372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔駛想潑冷水，不過覺得herman yeung同你地做既野好似差唔多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會係冷水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我地一直都有留意香港有冇類似嘅平台，所以當然有留意開 Herman Yeung。佢真係非常之有心，我地付出嘅極其量都係時間，佢就直頭放棄埋原本份人工。<br />\n<br />\nHerman Yeung 嘅片好多都好有質素，但我地喺影片設計、課題結構等好多細節都有自己諗法。數學科就係幫其他科試探呢啲諗法嘅先頭卒。<br />\n<br />\n另外我想讚多 Herman Yeung 一樣嘢，佢口齒真係好伶俐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地啲片係靠大量剪接先做到咁流暢，我本身講嘢係 1999。佢喺冇剪接嘅情況底下都可以講得咁順，呢樣我點學都學唔識。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n偶像herman yeung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家都煲緊佢啲天書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ee3f47c3869c4357da3fe201d351ef508752b4","tid":21862,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n幫左我好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5cdfc60147729ea30e2d80831dde2d7f3a20b5","tid":21862,"uid":41636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"多謝啊爸打 好受用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1199a94e77ac0fbf9aa3d6517517c594e006418","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"又再推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f63b1c7b209998cc3b15f47c68b273bf2dad3e5","tid":21862,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:49:40.000Z",