1dd975445081f6432ee128210cf","tid":21862,"uid":35448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"留名 + 幫推"},{"pid":"75c1bace4786e444fa00cd45983af75705c7efea","tid":21862,"uid":4946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打多謝你份心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時就冇乜大問題（或者只係我地察覺唔到），係有啲功能想加落去但唔識整。不過我地唔想貿貿然搵巴打你做義工，我地都過意唔去。<br />\n<br />\n反正而家都係 launch 咗冇耐，就比個平台運作一輪再作打算啦。話說有另一位巴打都專登 send email 過嚟話想幫手，好多謝你地咁有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我上年先至啱啱大學畢業，而家讀緊Master，咁既然你地都係免費教人，我都好樂意去同你地一齊搞搞個website，其實我而家係澳洲讀緊，依家去到二月中都係放緊summer break。所以呢段時間都好得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n遺憾巴打多謝你。你介唔介意 email 我地，或者我地喺 email 度傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncontact@project-identity.hk</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩幫手即管開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幫到手一定email巴打你"},{"pid":"998688cd95c39b7aaed71db8ff1e494f0d8b12d5","tid":21862,"uid":52832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩幫手即管開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幫到手一定email巴打你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你地，順便推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726e730995727f778ed76b084541dff000462ab6","tid":21862,"uid":3196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推，有咩要幫手開聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}